# CNNAlgosComparison

## Models For Comparison (All the models are written from scratch using pytorch)

2. Googlenet
3. ResNet
4. Mobilenet
5. Shufflenet
6. Squeezenet

- Retianl Disease Classification (https://www.kaggle.com/andrewmvd/retinal-disease-classification)
